        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Requiring human review for a \\$50 overage wastes approver time and delays legitimate low-risk requests. Configure the triage bot to auto-approve overages below \\$500 that meet a set of qualifying conditions: no prior denied exceptions in the current quarter, a plausible root cause (volume spike, not missing tags), and an optimisation plan that references at least one concrete action."
          }
