            "type": "text",
            "text": "A budget exception with a 2-hour SLA that takes 6 hours defeats its purpose. The triage bot must track open requests and escalate when an SLA is at risk. For P0 requests, escalation should happen at 90 minutes (30 minutes before the 2-hour SLA expires) \u2014 via PagerDuty or equivalent on-call routing, not just email."
          }
